<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Get a Quote - Heaps Arboriculture</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: #f7faf8;
    }

    .header {
      background: #f5ede4;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0d5c7;
    }

    .header h1 {
      color: #1a3c2e;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .header p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .page-container {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)),
                  url('data:image/url;base64,') center/cover no-repeat;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      padding: 60px 40px;
    }

    /* Background image styles */
    .page-container {
      background-image: url('tree-canopy-from-below.jpg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }

    .content-box {
      background: rgba(245, 237, 228, 0.95);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 48px;
      max-width: 500px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    }

    .content-box h2 {
      color: #1a3c2e;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .content-box p {
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      color: #1a3c2e;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .form-group input,
    .form-group textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #374151;
    }

    .form-group textarea {
      resize: vertical;
      min-height: 100px;
    }

    .button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px;
      background: #1a3c2e;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }

    .button:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .page-container {
        padding: 40px 20px;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .content-box {
        max-width: 100%;
        padding: 32px;
      }

      .content-box h2 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
  <h1>🌳 Get an Instant Quote</h1>
  <p>Professional arboricultural consultancy</p>
</div>

<div class="page-container">
  <div class="content-box">
    <h2>Start Your Project</h2>
    <p>Tell us about your trees and what you need. We'll provide a detailed, no-obligation quotation within 24 hours.</p>

    <form>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Your Name *</label>
        <input type="text" required placeholder="John Smith">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Email Address *</label>
        <input type="email" required placeholder="john@example.com">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Phone Number</label>
        <input type="tel" placeholder="020 XXXX XXXX">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Postcode *</label>
        <input type="text" required placeholder="NW1 2AB">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Tell us about your project *</label>
        <textarea required placeholder="Describe the trees, location, and what you need..."></textarea>
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="button">Get Quote →</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
